            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1.02%，報6618.04點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間19日10:36，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲67.01點（或1.02%），暫報6618.04點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-6.14%</li><li>近 1 月：-3.35%</li><li>近 3 月：+13.41%</li><li>近 6 月：+33.76%</li><li>今年以來：+30.46%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以科林研發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LRCX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LRCX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LRCX-US</a>)領漲。科林研發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LRCX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LRCX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LRCX-US</a>)上漲3.46%；安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)上漲2.89%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲2.73%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲2.58%；應用材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)上漲2.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)下跌0.27%；德州儀器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TXN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TXN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TXN-US</a>)下跌0.27%；超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)下跌0.08%；高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)下跌0%。</p></section></main>",
